  "description": "Adjust Gallery Card Image Border Radius\n\nModify the CSS styling for images within gallery card components to remove bottom border radius while maintaining top border radius.\n\nRequirements:\n- Target img elements inside .gallery-card-image containers\n- Set bottom-left and bottom-right border radius to 0\n- Preserve any existing top border radius values\n- Ensure the change applies consistently across all gallery card instances\n- Verify the visual appearance aligns with the card layout design\n- Test responsiveness across different screen sizes to ensure consistent rendering",
